cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY 

The paper deals with controlling embodied agents, which is a topic related to robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves machine learning techniques, specifically learning embeddings, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a sensor space and distance metric suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) may also be relevant. Finally, the concept of controlling agents with many degrees of freedom is related to control systems (cs.SY).
